006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.metaschema.binding;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.adapter.StringAdapter;
009import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.adapter.TokenAdapter;
010import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.adapter.UriAdapter;
011import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.IAttributable;
012import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.IBoundObject;
013import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.IMetaschemaData;
014import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.BoundFlag;
015import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.MetaschemaAssembly;
016
017import org.apache.commons.lang3.builder.ReflectionToStringBuilder;
018import org.apache.commons.lang3.builder.ToStringStyle;
019
020import java.net.URI;
021
022@SuppressWarnings({
023    "PMD.DataClass",
024    "PMD.FieldNamingConventions"
025})
026@MetaschemaAssembly(
027    formalName = "Property",
028    name = "property",
029    moduleClass = MetaschemaModelModule.class)
030public class Property implements IBoundObject {
031  private final IMetaschemaData __metaschemaData;
032
033  @BoundFlag(
034      formalName = "Property Name",
035      name = "name",
036      required = true,
037      typeAdapter = TokenAdapter.class)
038  private String _name;
039
040  @BoundFlag(
041      formalName = "Property Namespace",
042      name = "namespace",
043      defaultValue = IAttributable.DEFAULT_PROPERY_NAMESPACE,
044      typeAdapter = UriAdapter.class)
045  private URI _namespace;
046
047  @BoundFlag(
048      formalName = "Property Value",
049      name = "value",
050      required = true,
051      typeAdapter = StringAdapter.class)
052  private String _value;
053
054  public Property() {
055    this(null);
056  }
057
058  public Property(IMetaschemaData data) {
059    this.__metaschemaData = data;
060  }
061
062  @Override
063  public IMetaschemaData getMetaschemaData() {
064    return __metaschemaData;
065  }
066
067  public String getName() {
068    return _name;
069  }
070
071  public void setName(String value) {
072    _name = value;
073  }
074
075  public URI getNamespace() {
076    return _namespace;
077  }
078
079  public void setNamespace(URI value) {
080    _namespace = value;
081  }
082
083  public String getValue() {
084    return _value;
085  }
086
087  public void setValue(String value) {
088    _value = value;
089  }
090
091  @Override
092  public String toString() {
093    return new ReflectionToStringBuilder(this, ToStringStyle.MULTI_LINE_STYLE).toString();
094  }
095}
